Privacy Policy for NMC Prep
Last Updated: April 4, 2025

NMC Prep ("the App") is developed by Nahusha Investment ("we," "our," or "us"). This privacy policy explains how we handle user data.

1. Information We Collect
We do not collect, store, or share any personal user data.
Your privacy is important to us, and this app does not require or process any personal information.

2. Permissions Used
The App may request certain device permissions (e.g., internet access) only for its core functionality. However, no personal data is collected or stored.

3. Third-Party Services
We do not integrate third-party services (such as analytics, ads, or tracking tools) that collect personal data.

4. Future Changes
If we decide to collect user data in the future, we will:

Update this privacy policy accordingly.

Notify users about any data collection and obtain consent if required.

5. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, feel free to contact us at:
Email: nahushainvestment@gmail.com
